{
  "texts": [
    "There were 500 tweets collected in each API call with a wait time of 2 seconds between each call.",
    "The process consisted of using the search terms in the \"Ingest Tweets\" function of the engine to collect up to 500 tweets.",
    "These were subsequently written into a JSON file.",
    "If there was a next token, the engine would pause for 2 seconds before ingesting another set of tweets and writing another JSON file.",
    "This process continued until there was no next token."
  ]
}